original_title: PAW Patrol: Pups Save the Alien
overview: The PAW Patrol emBARKS on eight out-of-this-world adventures! An alien spaceship crash lands at Farmer Yumi's and the pups help the stranded extra-terrestrial fix his ship. Then, Rubble meets his double aboard an alien spaceship. Finally, Ryder and the pups save Mayor Goodway's party guests when a frightened alien zaps them into floating space bubbles and so much more!
title: PAW Patrol: Pups Save the Alien
